289d8258d7b3,Low,Reentrancy,['Violating CEI / Missing nonReentrant'],"<a name=""l-17""></a> Code does not follow the best practice of check-effects-interaction: Code should follow the best-practice of [CEI](https://blockchain-academy.hs-mittweida.de/courses/solidity-coding-beginners-to-intermediate/lessons/solidity-11-coding-patterns/topic/checks-effects-interactions/), where state variables are updated before any external calls are made. Doing so prevents a large class of reentrancy bugs."
